## Series Collection [/series{?limit,offset,filter,sort}]

### List all Series [GET]
+ Parameters
    + limit (optional, Number, `20`) ... max number of records to be returned.
    + offset (optional, Number, `0`) ... the starting point for retrieving data in the list.
    + filter (optional, String, `low`) ... two acceptable values for filter are: 'low' and 'high', which respectively result in returning series with low # of volumes (less than 6) and series with high # of volumes (for no filtering, don't pass/set this parameter).
    + sort (optional, String,, `asc`) ... two acceptable values for sort are: 'asc' and 'desc', which result in sorting series by title (for no sorting, don't pass/set this parameter).
 
