## Reviews Collection [/reviews{?limit,offset,filter,sort}]

### List all Reviews [GET]
+ Parameters
    + limit (optional, Number, `20`) ... max number of records to be returned.
    + offset (optional, Number, `0`) ... the starting point for retrieving data in the list.
    + filter (optional, String, `low`) ... two acceptable values for filter are: 'low' and 'high', which respectively result in returning reviews with low ratings (less than 2.5) and reviews with high ratings (for no filtering, don't pass/set this parameter).
